    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A–C. Habitus of Ceropales. A. Holotype male, Ceropales pallida sp. nov.; B. Female, C. pallida sp. nov; C. Female, C. maculata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6770936/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6770938>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A–B. Head of male in frontal view; A. Ceropales pallida sp. nov.; B. C. maculata. C–D. Head of female in dorsal view; C. Ceropales pallida sp. nov.; D. C. maculata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6770938/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6770940>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A–B. Genitalia, ventral view; A. Ceropales pallida sp. nov.; B. C. maculata. C–D. Subgenital plate (sternite 8) of male, dorsal view; C. Ceropales pallida sp. nov.; D. C. maculata. E–F. Subgenital plate (sternite 8) of male, lateral view; E. Ceropales pallida sp. nov.; F. C. maculata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6770940/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6770944>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. ID-tree of Ceropales from selected sequences of COI-5P markers, based on neighbor joining clustering, using the Kimura 2-parameter substitution model. Sample ID, sex, locality, sequence length, and their respective BINs are presented for each specimen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6770944/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6770946>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Distribution map for Ceropales pallida sp. nov. in Fennoscandia based on the studied material." ;
